{
  "text": "To determine the distress associated with the nightmares, a 5-point scale \"If you currently experience nightmares, how distressing are the nightmares?\" (0 = Not at all distressing, 1 = Not that distressing, 2 = Somewhat distressing, 3 = Quite distressing, and 4 = Very distressing) was presented. The item measuring nightmare frequency during childhood (\"How often did you experience nightmares during your childhood (from 6 to 12 year of age)?\") was of a similar eight-point format as the current nightmare frequency scale with retest reliability of r = .791 [CITATION_1] .",
